title: Nosleep Podcast S2E21
description:
It's episode 21 of the second season of The Nosleep Podcast!  The episode features five tales about strange sibling scares, childish games, and a tormented traveller.

This episode features these stories:

Say's Who? written by anonymous and read by Tyler Privett (Redditor maverick49er).

Children's Playground written by Arnie Kalkauskas (Redditor CryingCrow) and read by David Cummings (Redditor MikeRowPhone).

Baby Sister written by Leon Chan (Redditor straydog1980) and read by Michael McElroy (Redditor MikeTheInfidel).

The Devil's Breath written by Arjun Anand (Redditor ImAfraidOfMe) and read by David Cummings.

The Letter written by Hamish MacDonald (Redditor happy-jack) and read by Tyler Privett.
